  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to Healer Simulator RPG !</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/5b3a3751a3ba517087904c461d54e971.poster.avif?t=1747478007\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/5b3a3751a3ba517087904c461d54e971.webm?t=1747478007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/5b3a3751a3ba517087904c461d54e971.mp4?t=1747478007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can you help the sick townsfolk?</strong></p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/d73e487f6d1d0cef07309d14be7d7a8a.poster.avif?t=1747478007\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/d73e487f6d1d0cef07309d14be7d7a8a.webm?t=1747478007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/d73e487f6d1d0cef07309d14be7d7a8a.mp4?t=1747478007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will you solve all the mysteries?</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/8a2ab4b3fd9218a4d736aa4b4a424a20.poster.avif?t=1747478007\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/8a2ab4b3fd9218a4d736aa4b4a424a20.webm?t=1747478007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/8a2ab4b3fd9218a4d736aa4b4a424a20.mp4?t=1747478007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defeat your enemies?</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/4df6e782704ece5220ebf761125eab8d.poster.avif?t=1747478007\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/4df6e782704ece5220ebf761125eab8d.webm?t=1747478007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/4df6e782704ece5220ebf761125eab8d.mp4?t=1747478007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find out as exciting adventures and unexpected twists await you!</strong><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You are wounded. You are in pain. You feel hurt.</h2></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You jump into the portal...</i></p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/b48e6b46da473376bb12d51ed6b22d29.avif?t=1747478007\" width=254 height=254 /></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You wake up.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A broken amulet hangs around your neck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your memory is lost...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In front of you stands a girl.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She looks at you with caution and curiosity.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279640/extras/85a4583f2821853deab8e2d97e01c7e0.avif?t=1747478007\" width=254 height=254 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You feel the awakening of powers... Powers capable of healing others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But not you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What lies ahead?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Answers? Or...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Questions?..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Good luck! :)</strong></p><br>In this world, you are a mage with the power of healing magic!<br>You will uncover the mysteries of this world and heal those who are sick, injured, or suffering from psychological or physical issues<br>This is a <strong>Simulator</strong>, an <strong>Adventure</strong>, an <strong>RPG</strong>:<br><strong>This is Healer Simulator RPG</strong>",
